{"tid":2278654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反走私行動檢逾40貓狗　1隻貓死亡部分貓眼睛受傷","createTime":"2020-11-09T09:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T12:25:02.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3aa3138fa716c2e0bfa97c3c6f7abbf1e3c9fb6","tid":2278654,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"海關聯同水警在大嶼山北部水域展開反走私行動，檢獲40多萬支懷疑未完稅香煙，市值110萬元，應課稅值約77萬元。另外亦發現21個寵物膠籠，內藏34隻貓及9隻狗，其中一隻貓已死亡，全部未有植入晶片。<br />\n<br />\n海關及水警於凌晨4時許，發現5名可疑人士及一輛輕型貨車在大嶼山白芒徘徊，及後有一艘沒有著燈及載有貨物的快艇高速駛近岸邊，5名可疑人士發現執法人員追截，隨即跳上快艇離開，駛近東涌新發展碼頭附近上岸，再往東涌方向逃去。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559097-20201109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559097-20201109.htm&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=dfdb5ea1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559097-20201109.htm&h=80c00713\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559097-20201109.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1559097_1_20201109164705.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1559097_1_20201109164705.jpg&h=09605e33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a277631edc39c61f8b77282b60190670d468707d","tid":2278654,"uid":279357,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"捉十二個咁落力嘅<br />\n又飛機又快艇又軍艦<br />\n救四十個可以捉唔到人"}]}